.TH "CLISP" 1 "Last modified: 2004-03-14" "" "CLISP version 2.32.94"
.SH NAME
clisp \- ANSI Common Lisp compiler, interpreter and debugger.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.ad l
.hy 0
